      <odd id="aspace_f3556d130118b3de6ced74f96aefdcc2">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 46-A (YRG 46-A), Records and materials broadly documenting Yale buildings, facilities, and grounds.</p>  
      </odd>
